_sText:
ZOMG first map

16 spawns for each team, total of 32
The more players the better when playing

Notes:
There are 3 buyzones for both teams:
- the corner rooms they spawn in
- the two othe corner rooms (both t and ct buyzones)

The bottom of the map is dark intentionally, use it to your advantage! Although, beware, your enemy may be thinking the same thing!

This could make quite a good DeathMatch map.

Please do not share or edit this map without my permission
Ask via my FSPB account if you would like to make any changes or share this map
Thanks a bundle
